As of the date this torrent has been posted, this torrent contains all of the
music located at https://www.extrememusic.com/labels/18. This includes all of
the noise Two Steps From Hell has ever created, ranging from random thumping,
to their greatest hits. All songs are in 320 Kbps. Please note that only albums included on Extreme Music's website are included, thus excluding Archangel and Classics Vol. 2. Don't worry about this. The music in those albums are located in other included albums. To be more specific, the following albums are included:

All Drones go to Hell
All Drums go to Hell Vol. 1 Drums & Percussion
All Drums go to Hell Vol. 2 Drums & Percussion
Amaria
Ashes Vol. 1 Ethereal Drones
Ashes Vol. 2 Horror
